workzen.xgen.model.java
Class JavaClass

java.lang.Object
  workzen.xgen.model.java.JavaClass

public class JavaClass
extends java.lang.Object

This class stores metadata about a java class, including references and collections, and information about the corresponding sql table. It has a map of all the fields in the class, and knows which attributes are the primary key or transaction key.

Author:
Brad Matlack
